{"tid":1496220,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"警方：以「曱甴」形容示威者不理想　會了解","createTime":"2019-08-22T11:58:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-22T16:12:56.000Z","uid":212626,"like":4,"dislike":32,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"5c70081bc319f52bba0c865903901fb66af21be3","tid":1496220,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T11:58:33.000Z","msg":"警方昨日在元朗的驅散行動中，有警員通訊時，以「曱甴」形容示威者。警察公共關係科高級警司江永祥表示，有關用語不理想，會了解情況。<br />\n<br />\n江永祥又表示，他從來都有禮貌，警民溝通在乎互相尊重和有禮貌，例如他也會稱呼記者為「記者先生」及「記者小姐」。<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1476181-20190822.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1476181-20190822.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=eywEaFxHh3WcM61vPhP2LUoInKkgZqzseva8eQDkMF8%3D&h=94779b38\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1476181-20190822.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=d23844a3\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1476181-20190822.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"0de92888a78b9ce175aa780b7fb718e0e6eca9e5","tid":1496220,"uid":126099,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T11:59:08.000Z","msg":"收皮啦成日扮野"},{"pid":"06318b3fea104832ef692efe74a809677cd9ec4d","tid":1496220,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T12:00:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e9642dd9850255934b60009143382798d62e80c","tid":1496220,"uid":210677,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T12:00:42.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"66d218584f6e207ad4ff45f71db603d8b122acd6","tid":1496220,"uid":19527,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T12:00:45.000Z","msg":"自己都有叫啦扮哂野"},{"pid":"cb28dacbcdea5429c4f1eff6880bef104062ab7c","tid":1496220,"uid":997,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T12:01:12.000Z","msg":"